MESOSOMA. In lateral view 1.4 times as long as high, polished. Notaulix weakly distinct. Propodeum polished, close above lunule with short crenulae (
Fig. 5E
).

LEGS. Hind femur 3.8 times as long as broad (
Fig. 5F
). Claw downcurved, its basal lobe pointed (
Fig. 5G
