Body 2.6-3.2(-3.8) mm long. Antenna about as long as to somewhat longer than body and with 27-29 antennomeres. Flagellomeres long, 1.7-2 times longer than broad. Head in dorsal view 1.75-1.8 times as broad as long; temple either rounded (
Fig. 5B
) or slightly receded (cf. 
